values:
London. Dorset. Chesire. Northampton. 4 hours away at best.
What the hell am I going to do without you?

<center>Here's to you and your lover boy...</center>

2 weekends. He probably doesn't even realise. But all the same...feels harsh. I seriously hate rifle. Good for him that he loves it so much but I hate it. And I hate 99% of the people that go there. 0_o
I'm in a shitty mood. I also have PMT. I want to go shopping...I'm sick of working on this lame ass dissertation. I have no idea if I'm writing my literature review right. *huff* I might go home.
